data.name: Air Fryer Sweet Potato Wedges
data.quickTastyDescription: Crispy on the outside and soft on the inside, these sweet potato wedges are a delicious and healthy snack or side dish!
detailedCookingInstructions: Wash and peel the sweet potatoes, then cut them into wedges.
In a large bowl, toss the sweet potato wedges with olive oil, salt, black pepper, and paprika until evenly coated.
Place the sweet potato wedges in a single layer in the air fryer basket.
Cook for 20-25 minutes, shaking the basket halfway through, until golden and crispy.
Remove from the air fryer and serve hot. Enjoy!
data.detailedName: Easy Air Fryer Sweet Potato Wedges
data.modifiersForBase: Seasoned with olive oil and spices
